Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:17.30,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}一定才剛剛開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:24.01,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}千里之行始於足下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:30.98,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}一開始的時候無論是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:38.52,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}都不可以恐慌  這才是最重要的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:47.80,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}選擇了自己所喜歡的道路真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:55.01,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,600)}神啊  我要因此而感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:03.31,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)}如今的Lucky  請好好地珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:06.58,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Happy並持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:10.40,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}來吧  保持著這股勢頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:13.24,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Bang！Bang！Bang！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:15.41,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是呢  Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:19.00,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如今正是時候  Happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.06,0:23:22.13,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}把握住機會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:27.30,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}努力地生活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.55,0:00:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2035年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八月三十一日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,aloha～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：aloha為夏威夷土著人的問候語）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大家的禮物夏威夷果巧克力已經平安到達了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  還有SOKOICHIGO的手機掛件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在夏威夷也有SOKOICHIGO…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我知錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:53.00,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正准圆简体}夏天的結束(byebye)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假就要  結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業都有  好好做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油  Fight  噢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快來看  快來看  這片沙灘真是好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊  果然沒人在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連本以為很長的暑假都… 真是光陰似箭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦碰了面  果不其然又轉換到了遊玩模式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起來  第一學期的休學式上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就在一個月後  9月1日再見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:41.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}9月1日聖櫻學園祭網\N直臨決戰最終更新版本大公開！\N前夜祭活動內容發表！\N新遊戲！\N全體學生參加計劃開始！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待度好高啊  但只有一個月的時間嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小意思小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本應該是這樣的  可…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰說甚麼小意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己  你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點起來  睡著了會掛的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經這樣過了兩天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也難怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  你們停一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼章魚是蟲字旁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:22.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日語「章魚」漢字也寫作「蛸」）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個算蟲子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼青魚不加魚字旁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都把青魚當笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到件好事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來變換一下房間佈局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大躍進！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變了佈局的話  一定能萬事OK的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個辦法了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子挪個位置甚麼的就能大躍進了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  你們不覺得這裡空出來超不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就風水學來說  α波也噴湧而出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（α波：即Alpha波，8—14赫茲，精神集中時，冥想狀態亦是此種狀態。\N靈感或自覺敏銳，腦的活動活躍。）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來  一切都能順利無阻的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也只有這個辦法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  小矮人先生你也是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  是吧  沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  學美…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前衝～向前衝～…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛  好痛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學…學美壞掉了  怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來  睡著了會掛的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該醒過來的…是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑  快想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把事情推給別人真不像個男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法…小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視嗎  又無視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前衝～向前衝～…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明是個大男人還穿著裙子  不害臊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊  不要脫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你以為這樣能贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起學姐  我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是你給我上了一課才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我說一句行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們忘記了一件很重要的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:07:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我說咯  暑假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  這樣下去大家都會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  都會死蹺蹺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  所以我提議大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  輪流休息一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在喜歡的地方寫上名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來也很麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快看快看  這間餐廳的東西真的很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖洋洋的真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想去海邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  就是暑假的最後一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過得真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來之後  我就一個人站在陌生的馬路上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然拼命找過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻從哪裡都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這裡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一臉幸福的模樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底夢到甚麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼讓她再躺一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點睡著了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這不就是你一直想買的那件T恤嘛  買下了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:09:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  用上個月的工資買的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯啊  我也不要讀書算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～出社會上班真的很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都像趕廟會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是聖櫻坂站  聖櫻坂站到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  應該是這個吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是重新看起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美最喜歡吃抹茶紅豆冰了  她一定會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子學姐真是一個美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹茶紅豆冰最棒  我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的慰問品  多佳子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:12:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼  我看了聖櫻網的營運日誌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得你們好象一直住在學校的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為謝禮  就讓你欣賞一下夏威夷的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的海灘和餐廳…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說  愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸的學生會長大人今天是來偵查的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又是我一個人在說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  又是我在自說自話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是聖櫻網的管理員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有苗頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有苗頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點事想和學美同學談一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要在這裡做一個很大很大的門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為材料是在建材超市統一訂購的  稍微便宜了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們預定在那裡放置食品攤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在那邊有烤栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是2-C的羽田她們的店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是1-B的美和的店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有2-D的山本她們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊則是新城她們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣場上還有工藤  渡邊還有澤村她們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  你全都記住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是各個店鋪的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳給我們點了一把火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們每天都很愉快  這都是虧了多佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再帶你逛逛那邊  跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合併？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確地說是吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生數量不斷減少  經營停滯不前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時代還是這麼漫不經心的話  會變成這樣也不奇怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是不是保留聖櫻的名字之類的細節還沒有決定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之聖櫻學園將會被我們愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸學園合併吸收掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和聖櫻學生會長有私交不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這有甚麼關係嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們打算中止學園祭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個正是聖櫻學園愚昧的經營的縮影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單純的一時興起  只在乎眼前的一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個完全沒有意義的慶典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太突然了  至少等到明年…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們還處在計劃階段  應該沒有任何實際損失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大量學生  為了追求更有趣的生活而離開學校的狀態下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然選擇學生的身份的你們現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉辦這種單純的慶典究竟有甚麼意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個消息預定在九月一日公佈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前請準備好學生會長的發言稿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  這個情報絕對不能外流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上原同學  輸入的資料有很明顯的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意準確性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:17:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一發
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很久之前就對學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐這個騙子！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙…  騙子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  多佳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒有辦法招待你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美同學你們為甚麼這麼拼命呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是因為很愉快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是要做很多的準備嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話大家看到這個就會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽真是害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…誒  徹頭徹尾無視我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下的話就能一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我有點必須做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧彆扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Byebye  多佳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能看到學美同學腦海中的影像…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡  有著我們學園的學生所唯獨做不到的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許那個答案就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:14.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天的營業就此結束  歡迎再次使用）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是理事長嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:26.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（夏天結束  完成  去游泳池放煙火）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑也下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得自己還在做著那個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並不是夢  而會一直繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要想到這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得特別高興！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.75,0:23:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八話  『戰鬥吧聖櫻學生會！』
